Amelia-Jane Harris used to weigh 27st 10lbs and was a size 32 . 
  She developed Crohn's disease and lost 18 stone in 20 months to become a slim size 6 . 
  But she says her new 'dream body' is a nightmare as she cannot eat and vomits daily . 
  She was bullied at school and was called 'Fatty Bum Bum' The illness has seen her lose more than 18 stone (252lbs) She now weighs 8st 9lbs (121lbs) and says she is in constant pain and cannot eat . 
 